Motorists are warned to avoid the R81 road towards Mooketsi. The road is currently being blocked by local residents in the area due to protest actions. Especially motorists on their way to Modjadjiskloof, Giyani and Polokwane (R81) are cautioned. The newspaper was able to confirm that a task team from the provincial police are currently en-route to the scene. This is a developing story and more details will be published as information becomes available. If some of our readers are in the area, please let us know about your experiences by sending info or photographs to isabel@zoutnet.co.za or via WhatsApp to 073Â 349 1587.